    "notes": "Detection should correlate EID 10 (lsass access with GrantedAccess containing 0x10 VM_READ bit) with the source process path — high-confidence signal when source is outside System32/ProgramFiles and CallTrace includes non-system modules. Chaining EID 10 → EID 11 (.dmp file write) within a short time window from the same PID dramatically reduces false positives. Key exclusions: MsMpEng.exe, csrss.exe, werfault.exe, svchost.exe under SYSTEM context accessing lsass are routine."
